---
title: Roast Cauliflower & Feta Salad with Pearl Couscous & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Like a soft teddy bear, tonight’s dish is fluffy and calming. Tufts of roasted cauliflower and other warm veggies poke out of a golden pearl couscous. Mixed with creamy feta on top, it will be like eating a very tasty cloud.
